LANGUAGE

git status for each file
in stage
in the workspace

stdin is standard input


OPTIONS

-d keep dots when picking

-a show all matches when picking/gicking

-p plain path, do not pick
	before it was -n, but that was never easy to remember
	maybe it is not needed?

-s consider stage files
-w consider workspace files

-c cut off status
-v show status, verbose

-D dryrun/debug